➜卡梅隆计划挑战“挑战者深渊”
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=28617	24600
泰坦尼克号和阿凡达的导演计划要<a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/08/science/earth/james-cameron-prepares-to-dive-into-mariana-trench.html">挑战</a>世界上最深的海沟：<a href="http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%8C%91%E6%88%98%E8%80%85%E6%B7%B1%E6%B8%8A">挑战者深渊</a>。<i>
